---
title: Amazing Apricot Chicken with Roasted Potatoes & Green Beans
description: Chicken breasts are a reliable go-to for dinner—easy to cook and pleasing to just about every palate. But let’s face it: they can be a little bit humdrum sometimes. Which is why we’ve enlisted the help of an apricot sauce to bring them out of their doldrums. It coats each bite of meat in jammy stone-fruit sweetness and even tastes great drizzled over the potatoes and roasted green beans on the side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ec3dcefd0919460553b6376-85f77c4b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/amazing-apricot-chicken-5ec3dcefd0919460553b6376-34ca0b2e.pdf
author: HelloFresh
time required: 35 minutes
course: main course
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/amazing-apricot-chicken-5ec3dcefd0919460553b6376
cuisine: North America
